ory pilot workshops.\n        </p>\n\n        {clauses.map((clause) => (\n          <div key={clause.title} className=\"p-8 rounded-[24px] border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/60 backdrop-blur-[12px] space-y-4\">\n            <h2 className=\"text-[18px] font-semibold text-white tracking-tight\">{clause.title}</h2>\n            <p className=\"text-white/70 leading-[1.7]\">{clause.text}</p>\n          </div>\n        ))}\n      </div>\n    </InnerPageShell>\n  );\n}","new_text":"\"use client\";\n\nimport React, { useState } from \"react\";\nimport InnerPageShell from \"@/components/inner-pages/InnerPageShell\";\nimport InnerPageHero from \"@/components/inner-pages/InnerPageHero\";\nimport PremiumCTA from \"@/components/inner-pages/PremiumCTA\";\nimport { Lock, CheckCircle2, Send } from \"lucide-react\";\n\nexport default function NdaPage() {\n  const [submitted, setSubmitted] = useState(false);\n  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(false);\n\n  const steps = [\n    { num: \"01\", title: \"Initiate Request\", desc: \"Submit your corporate legal name and Preferred Jurisdictional settings.\" },\n    { num: \"02\", title: \"Automated Draft\", desc: \"Our compliance parser compiles a standardized Mutual NDA tailored to your region.\" },\n    { num: \"03\", title: \"Execute & Lock\", desc: \"Digital signatures are completed. All shared contexts are sealed in enclaves.\" }\n  ];\n\n  return (\n    <InnerPageShell>\n      <InnerPageHero\n        category=\"Legal & Compliance\"\n        title=\"Mutual NDA Protocol\"\n        highlightedWord=\"Protocol\"\n        description=\"Learn how GFF AI secures early-stage sandbox investigations, safeguards proprietary designs, and executes mutual non-disclosure agreements.\"\n      />\n\n      <div className=\"max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-16 pb-24 space-y-12 relative z-10\">\n        <div className=\"p-6 rounded-[24px] border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/60 backdrop-blur-[12px] space-y-3\">\n          <h2 className=\"text-[18px] font-semibold text-white tracking-tight flex items-center gap-2\">\n            <Lock className=\"w-4 h-4 text-[#E4000F]\" /> Reciprocal Confidentiality Protection\n          </h2>\n          <p className=\"text-white/70 leading-relaxed text-[13px] font-light\">\n            Before we demonstrate bespoke multi-agent sandboxes or evaluate database schemas in our Garage phase, GFF AI secures reciprocal confidentiality. Our Mutual NDA is engineered to safeguard proprietary codebases, vector weights, model parameters, and corporate credentials.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\">\n          {steps.map((step, idx) => (\n            <div key={idx} className=\"p-6 rounded-[24px] border border-white/5 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#08080a] to-[#010101] relative overflow-hidden group\">\n              <span className=\"absolute top-4 right-4 text-[42px] font-mono font-bold leading-none text-white/5\">{step.num}</span>\n              <h4 className=\"text-[15px] font-semibold text-white tracking-tight mt-2\">{step.title}</h4>\n              <p className=\"mt-2 text-[12px] leading-relaxed text-white/50 font-light\">{step.desc}</p>\n            </div>\n          ))}\n        </div>\n\n        <div className=\"p-6 rounded-[24px] border border-white/5 bg-[#030304]/80 max-w-xl mx-auto space-y-4\">\n          <div className=\"space-y-1 text-center\">\n            <span className=\"inline-flex px-2.5 py-0.5 text-[9px] font-mono tracking-widest text-[#009DFF] border border-[#009DFF]/25 bg-[#009DFF]/5 rounded-full uppercase\">Request Portal</span>\n            <h3 className=\"text-[18px] font-semibold text-white tracking-tight\">Initiate Mutual NDA Draft</h3>\n          </div>\n\n          {submitted ? (\n            <div className=\"py-6 text-center space-y-3\">\n              <CheckCircle2 className=\"w-10 h-10 text-green-500 mx-auto\" />\n              <p className=\"text-white/80 text-[13px] font-light\">Our legal team will email your custom bilateral NDA draft to the specified address within 4 business hours.</p>\n            </div>\n          ) : (\n            <form onSubmit={(e) => { e.preventDefault(); setLoading(true); setTimeout(() => { setLoading(false); setSubmitted(true); }, 1000); }} className=\"space-y-3\">\n              <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3\">\n                <input required placeholder=\"Corporate Legal Name\" className=\"w-full px-4 py-2 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-black/60 text-[12px] text-white focus:outline-none\" />\n                <input type=\"email\" required placeholder=\"Authorized Officer Email\" className=\"w-full px-4 py-2 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-black/60 text-[12px] text-white focus:outline-none\" />\n              </div>\n              <select className=\"w-full px-4 py-2 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-black/60 text-[12px] text-white/80 focus:outline-none\">\n                <option>Delaware, United States</option>\n                <option>England & Wales</option>\n                <option>Singapore (SGX Compliant)</option>\n              </select>\n              <button type=\"submit\" className=\"w-full py-2.5 rounded-xl text-[12px] font-semibold text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-[#E4000F] to-[#009DFF] hover:opacity-95 flex items-center justify-center gap-1.5\">\n                {loading ? \"Processing Secure Ticket...\" : <><Send className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" /> Request NDA Review</>}\n              </button>\n            </form>\n          )}\n        </div>\n\n        <PremiumCTA\n          title=\"Preparing for an architectural audit session?\"\n          description=\"Schedule a technical workspace review to understand how your proprietary parameters are compartmentalized within private sandboxes.\"\n          primaryLabel=\"Contact Legal Desk\"\n          primaryHref=\"/contact?pathway=nda\"\n          secondaryLabel=\"Review Trust Specs\"\n          secondaryHref=\"/privacy\"\n        />\n      </div>\n    </InnerPageShell>\n  );\n}"}}}
